  "instructions": [
    "Heat ghee in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Sauté onion and garlic until softened, about 3 minutes.",
    "Add curry powder and cumin powder, cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add fenugreek leaves, sauté until wilted, about 2 minutes.",
    "Add rice and fry-grind-rice-khao-khua to the saucepan, stir to combine.",
    "Add lemon juice and salt, stir to combine.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a heatproof bowl.",
    "Cover the bowl with a clean cloth and let it rest for 5 minutes to allow the flavors to meld.",
    "Fluff the pilaf with a fork and serve hot.",
    "Serve the Springy Ethiopian Fry-Grind-Rice-Khao-Khua Pilaf with your favorite Ethiopian dishes."
